body:
Please don&#039;t match me twice with someone I just had a game with or against &amp; please don&#039;t match me with people I just reported for being toxic. Most of the time it&#039;s someone who goes 0/something and they are tilted and on a loss streak. Keep in mind that I had someone like this that was toxic, I reported them and still got stuck with them in the next game. Are you serious this has happened me 3 to 4 times the past week and I lost my promos to plat and now I&#039;m just tanking so hard. Its like Riot is trying to tilt me. HOLY. Can I just get a whole new team lol stop this. Like one time I won against a pantheon who went 0/11 then the next game I got him on my team.. thank goodness that was a remake. I&#039;m already not doing too hot this ranked season but this is not helping at all. Riot, are you trying to tilt me? 
{{sticker:sg-janna}} 
Also something I&#039;m seeing a lot in my games...people that don&#039;t know how to ward. Blitz supp at 50 min in only had placed like 10 wards all game and that&#039;s because I had to tell him to ward looool gold is really this bad still.. what? Trinkets are free like use them haha especially if you are support. I just want decent teams, it&#039;s so hard to get nowadays...

replies.body:
Yeah, the sticker ^^. Lets  mirror your argument. You said you see a lot of people wich don´t  know how to ward. I would expect more wards from someone who blame others for that. Even you are right with the Blitz, a sup must ward much more.  I don´t wanted to annoy you. I just tried friendly (personally I like stickers) to remind you that everyone can do better.  {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

My elo is there because I rarely play ranked and just have fun in normals. I startet with LoL in march last year and just wanted a silver border. So I stopped ranked in august as I reached it.

have a nice time :)
